{"type":"message","id":"bed141d3","parentId":"7e9440b9","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:01:34.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done — I rewrote the doctor agent’s core `.md` files into the same cleaner, more concise style as the patient-facing one, while preserving LoopBot’s existing medical role, triage behavior, tone, and safety logic. If you want, I can also make `USER.md` and the doctor-side files feel even more stylistically matched line-for-line.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0640547bea7e55330169b3ee8cdb8c8191bdc8f21574fb240d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":217,"output":83,"cacheRead":11520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11820,"cost":{"input":0.0005425,"output":0.001245,"cacheRead":0.0028799999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0046675}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773399691879}}
